Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://dotnet.microsoft.com/

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
# Runtime deps mirror image/dotnet/debian-13/.dotnet.inc.yaml. Hardcoded because
# dh_shlibdeps is skipped for the prebuilt Microsoft runtime binaries.
Conflicts: dotnet-runtime-8, dotnet-runtime-9, dotnet-runtime-10
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ca-certificates,
 libc6,
 libgcc-s1,
 libgssapi-krb5-2,
 libicu76,
 libssl3t64,
 libstdc++6,
 tzdata,
 zlib1g
Description: .NET @MAJOR_VERSION@ runtime
 Microsoft .NET runtime for the @MAJOR_VERSION@ release line, installed under
 /usr/lib/dotnet with /usr/bin/dotnet on PATH (FHS layout).

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-oci-config
Architecture: all
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: OCI configuration for @PACKAGE_NAME@
 OCI container configuration (DOTNET_ROOT, DOTNET_VERSION, and PATH) for the
 @PACKAGE_NAME@ package.
